      <link>https://www.instagram.com/p/C__Ete_odhv/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/625955013_1660612904821719_909437155661364627_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_s360x360_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=109&amp;ig_cache_key=MzQ1ODUwMzQwODk3MDk1MDM4Nw%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjEwODB4MTA4MC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=-jQpiqBAzM4Q7kNvwERoqm0&amp;_nc_oc=AdoeoRVMpUbclaUDDsFM38mJFcuxa3Sj0Lni-hV2OOVVfs2vSiad-jfazRAjSEIXuVg&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=w6JLcIFXwcfdBIoqiXaOrg&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfwncFHrFg-qnrvYxDS_UFzagQ-teS96igEfdbTdpA0dQA&amp;oe=69C8F512" alt="Instagram billede fra @andreiongd" /></p><p><strong>@andreiongd</strong></p><p>&quot;BIELKE&amp;YANG&quot;<br/>
<br/>
In collaboration with Oslo based studio @bielkeyang to explore their ampersand logo. The idea was to take the logo and reimagine it as digital and experimental, while still retaining the original identity. The studio is in the process of redesigning their website and wanted different outputs that could be used digitally for web and physically for their new office. Inspired by their new light installation, I created a custom tool with a flexible design system that allows the studio to customise the output, allowing for endless variations.<br/>
